### How to fix

One simple approach is just to change the record into a custom type. For example, the above bad example can be changed to:

    type MyRecord
        = MyRecord
            { oneField : Int
            , anotherField : String
            , yetAnotherField : Bool
            , andAnotherField : Int
            , andAnotherField2 : Int
